参加了一件衬衫这是2005年电影<em>橡胶约翰尼（Johnny</em> ）的剧照，他用aphex twin制作了剧照。</p><p>与艺术家的其他合作伙伴关系包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supreme-announce-janes-addiction-fashion-collection-3808098">与简的成瘾合作</a>，该成瘾于去年10月下降，并在2021年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/massive-attack-supreme-collaboration-2970668">受到攻击风格的服装系列</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3839030" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3839030" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3839030" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000.jpg" alt="Aphex双胞胎，“窗户”艺术品" width="2000" height="2003" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000-400x401.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000-800x801.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000-696x697.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000-1392x1394.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/aphex-twin@2000x2000-1068x1070.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3839030" class="wp-caption-text"> Aphex双胞胎，“窗户”艺术品。 </figcaption></figure><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Aphex Twin -Windowlicker（官方视频）1080p HD" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UBS4Gi1y_nc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在此之前，有来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supreme-smiths-inspired-fall-fashion-range-2535573">史密斯（Smiths）</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-supreme-collection-featuring-velvet-underground-album-art-2548705">天鹅绒（Velvet）</a>等人的启发的收藏，2015年，Supreme Tap <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/neil-young-29-1208369">Neil Young</a>进行了合作，出售了一件T恤，上面有一张Young本人穿着最高品牌衬衫的照片。</p><p>在其他Aphex Twin News中，早在12月，艺术家<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-surprise-releases-new-compilation-music-from-the-merch-desk-2016-2023-3822843">就惊喜发行了一份新的汇编，称为“来自Merch Desk（2016-2023）”</a> 。</p><p>他于2023年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-announces-new-ep-shares-first-track-blackbox-life-recorder-21f-3458933">在Room7 F760&#39;EP中发布了他的“ Blackbox Life Recorder 21F /”</a> ，这是他五年来的第一首新音乐。该系列还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-launches-new-augmented-reality-app-3484622">产生了自己的增强现实应用程序</a>。然后，他在第二个月份放弃了EP&#39;London 19.08.2023&#39;，与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-and-bonobo-to-headline-field-day-2023-buy-tickets-3385769#:~:text=The%20date%20%E2%80%93%20August%2019%2C%202023,show%20in%202019%20at%20Printworks.">他在伦敦2023年的《田野日》（Field Day）的头条表演</a>相吻合。</p><p>自2014年获得<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/grammys">格莱美奖（Grammy Award</a> ）以来，Aphex Twin尚未发行全长录音室专辑。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/supreme-and-aphex-twin-team-up-for-windowlicker-collab-shirt-3839023">最高和Aphex Twin团队为“ Windowlicker”合作衬衫组成，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
